            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Gaius Nerius Severus, son of Gaius, of tribe Quirina, aedile, quaestor for the res publica, quaestor of the alimenta, flamen Augustalis,
                   curator of the New Claudian road, prefect for administering justice. Gaius Nerius Iustus, his most sweet brother, and Illyrica Philumene, his most
                   unhappy wife, set this up.
